form.current-chamber: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES
form.official-title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3979.

section.text: That, in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3979, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall make the following correction: In section 1207(e)(2), strike categories I, II, III, VII, and X and insert categories I, II, III, VII, X, XI, and XIII.

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives December 10, 2014.
